[FILE:199:descriptions/desc.primary]
Libmikmod is the library powering the portable Mikmod module audio player. 
It supports the IT, XM, S3M, MTM, 669, STM, ULT, FAR, MED, AMF, DSM, IMF, 
GDM, STX, OKT and of course MOD module formats.


